sentences: Line Dissing Karred Larsen (born 1 November 1996, in Skagen) known as Line (pronounced lee-neh in Danish), is a Danish singer.
On the final held on 23 March 2012, she finished as the runner-up, with 38.3% of the public vote, behind Ida, who carried the title with 61.7%.
Immediately after the win, Line released her winning song as her debut single appearing which reached straight to No. 3 in its week of release.
